Detailed Description

Contains phone signal strength related information. 

 // Use PhoneStateListener to get SignalStrength information,
 void myPhoneStateListener::onSignalStrengthsChanged(const gaia::telephony::SignalStrength& signalStrength) {
      // Get information of it
      signalStrength.getGsmSignalStrength();
